at a stroke.

243
00:13:29,599 --> 00:13:31,908
Yes, or indeed, at a strike.

244
00:13:32,079 --> 00:13:33,307
Yes. ¿What?

245
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:37,313
I would be wholeheartedly
in favourof such a move.

246
00:13:37,479 --> 00:13:39,276
Itwould be a splendid economy.

247
00:13:39,439 --> 00:13:42,431
And show great political courage
to sack staff

248
00:13:42,599 --> 00:13:45,716
in depressed
marginal constituencies.

249
