There is nowhere
we can cut down.

250
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:54,032
- I see waste everywhere.
- I agree with you, Minister.

251
00:13:54,199 --> 00:13:56,759
- There is scope foreconomy...
- Well, where?

252
00:13:56,999 --> 00:14:00,469
Well. I sometimes feel
that the very way we do things

253
00:14:00,639 --> 00:14:03,995
is on too lavish a scale.
