00:16:29,439 --> 00:16:30,713
Top left.

301
00:16:31,479 --> 00:16:33,197
Bernard! Come in here!

302
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:35,878
Now!

303
00:16:38,799 --> 00:16:42,997
