304
00:16:43,159 --> 00:16:45,593
- What thing?
- The Business Efficiency Exhibition!

305
00:16:46,239 --> 00:16:48,958
I do apologise,
but whatwith the...

306
00:16:49,119 --> 00:16:51,428
staff economies
in yourprivate office,

307
00:16:51,599 --> 00:16:54,238
it is awfully difficult
to keep track.

308
00:16:54,399 --> 00:16:57,596
- What's happening this afternoon?
- I'll get the diary.

309
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:02,033
Not now, dear!

310
00:17:03,159 --> 00:17:04,387
Not now!

311
00:17:10,039 --> 00:17:13,156
- Morning, duck.
- Do you have to do that now?

312
00:17:13,319 --> 00:17:16,550
Yes. Yes. They've cancelled
the night shift.

313
00:17:16,719 --> 00:17:20,268
Some idiot's started another
of those economy drives.

