00:17:21,879 --> 00:17:24,154
- I'm Nellie.
- Good. Well, the point is...

315
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,547
Who are you?

316
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,598
I'm the Minister.

317
00:17:28,239 --> 00:17:30,799
Oh, really?

318
00:17:31,999 --> 00:17:36,629
Oh, I'm everso pleased to meet you.
I voted foryou.

319
00:17:36,799 --> 00:17:38,755
