- Er... Jim.

323
00:17:45,159 --> 00:17:47,036
Here's the diary, Minister.

324
00:17:47,199 --> 00:17:49,838
Right.
Turn that off, would you, dear?

325
00:17:49,999 --> 00:17:51,910
Turn it... Nellie!

326
00:17:52,919 --> 00:17:53,988
What?

327
00:17:54,159 --> 00:17:56,309
Would you excuse us?
