328
00:17:56,479 --> 00:17:59,152
I've got to get on you know, Jim.

329
00:17:59,719 --> 00:18:00,868
So have I.

330
00:18:02,199 --> 00:18:03,199
Jim?

331
00:18:03,919 --> 00:18:05,910
Well, I won't use the hoover.

332
00:18:06,079 --> 00:18:08,673
I'll tiptoe, you'll nevernotice me.

333
00:18:08,839 --> 00:18:11,034
- Go please.
- I'm light as a feather.

334
00:18:11,199 --> 00:18:12,951
Go! Now!

335
00:18:17,639 --> 00:18:19,118
All right, Jim.

336
00:18:19,359 --> 00:18:20,997
I can take a hint.

337
00:18:26,199 --> 00:18:31,193
