our Directorof Manpower Planning.

338
00:18:31,439 --> 00:18:34,033
- Brough?
- Yes, staff reductions.

339
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:37,908
- Oh, yes.
- And then straight to the House.

340
00:18:38,079 --> 00:18:41,958
At 8 o'clock the French Prime
Minister's reception at his Embassy.

341
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:45,509
I must take the schedules down
to the Whips Office.

342
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:50,156
- Bernard...
- Yes, Minister?

343
00:18:50,319 --> 00:18:51,877
It is worth it, you know...

344
00:18:52,039 --> 00:18:54,428
Centre page spread
and three pictures.

345
00:18:54,599 --> 00:18:56,271
Yes, I have read it, Minister.

346
00:18:57,759 --> 00:19:01,388
See this one of me, with a cheese roll
on a cardboard plate?

347
00:19:02,719 --> 00:19:05,552
"No luxury lunches in Hacker's
new austerity regime".

348
00:19:05,719 --> 00:19:08,597
"Economy begins at home"
said Jim Hackertoday,

