00:19:13,599 --> 00:19:16,477
- Terrific, isn't it?
- You have read it to me already.

352
00:19:16,919 --> 00:19:19,433
- Great, isn't it?
- Yes, Minister.

353
00:19:21,719 --> 00:19:24,153
Economise on the beaches...

