00:19:25,999 --> 00:19:27,557
- Excuse me.
- Yes? Yes?

355
00:19:27,719 --> 00:19:30,438
- I'd like to see the Minister.
- Do you have an appointment?

356
00:19:30,599 --> 00:19:32,555
Ron Watson, General Secretary

357
00:19:32,719 --> 00:19:36,029
of the Union of Civil Service
Transport Workers.

358
00:19:36,199 --> 00:19:38,588
- Yes, Mr. Watson.
- We're disturbed about rumours

359
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:41,319
of redundancies
affecting ourmembers...

360
00:19:41,479 --> 00:19:43,993
I'm sorry, you must have
an appointment.

361
00:19:44,159 --> 00:19:46,878
- Phone me tomorrow.
- Why can't I arrange it now?

362
00:19:47,039 --> 00:19:48,472
- I'm sorry.
- Oh, really!

363
00:19:48,639 --> 00:19:52,109
Mandy, make an appointment
for Mr. Watson fornextweek.

364
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:53,279
Nextweek?

365
00:19:53,439 --> 00:19:55,350
Hello... Mr. Brough.

