- 100 % response.

419
00:22:39,239 --> 00:22:41,434
How could you allow this
to happen?

420
00:22:41,599 --> 00:22:42,918
C. B. E., Minister.

421
00:22:43,919 --> 00:22:44,988
C. B. E?

422
00:22:45,159 --> 00:22:46,638
Can't be everywhere.

423
00:22:49,039 --> 00:22:51,314
Of course,
in normal circumstances...

424
00:22:51,479 --> 00:22:53,515
Yes. Yes. I know, I know.

425
00:22:54,119 --> 00:22:57,316
You and Mrs. Hackerare due
at the French Embassy at 8.

426
00:22:58,159 --> 00:23:00,878
Oh, yes.
