- Just "overwrought".

455
00:26:18,199 --> 00:26:20,349
"Overwrought as a newt",
actually.

456
00:26:22,159 --> 00:26:23,990
It couldn't really be any worse.

457
00:26:24,359 --> 00:26:26,077
I don'twant to depress you...

458
00:26:26,439 --> 00:26:29,192
but there is just this lead story
in The Times.

459
00:26:30,399 --> 00:26:31,593
It is worse!

460
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:35,877
"Hackerrecruit 400 new Civil Servants
in, quote, "economy drive"!

461
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:38,758
