- You asked forthem.

462
00:26:38,919 --> 00:26:41,513
You demanded a complete study,
facts and figures.

463
00:26:41,679 --> 00:26:44,068
These measures cannot be taken
with non people.

464
00:26:44,239 --> 00:26:47,914
If you create more jobs,
more people have to be employed.

465
00:26:48,079 --> 00:26:49,353
It's common sense.

466
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:52,511
If you persistwith the
Bureaucratic Watchdog Office,

467
00:26:52,679 --> 00:26:55,671
